        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Let me ask you—the Eden that you envision... what is it like?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Equal, free, safe...', 3: '16', 4: 'Just like the one you envision, I think.', 5: '17'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": 18,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Ha. I guess we\\'re similar, aren\\'t we?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'What a crafty answer.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'The apocalypse hasn\\'t ended, not just because of the Punishing Virus or the war... It\\'s because of the humans. Because of human nature.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'The exploiters and the exploited, the oppressors and the oppressed... those who make choices, and those who get their choices taken away... This... loop, it never ends.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Eventually... they don\\'t even lie about it anymore, those prideful bastards.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'But no one has the right to decide someone else\\'s fate. No one gets to say who lives or dies, who stays, and who is left behind.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '8'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Closing your eyes so you can\\'t see, trying to forget if you did see... Running away if you can\\'t forget. Up there, far away, with everything you would forsake.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: '...Better to stand where the world refuses to face, to challenge it, to create a real \"Eden\".', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '...Why would you fight so hard for that?', 3: '27', 4: 'You\\'re the idealist, aren\\'t you?', 5: '28'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": 29,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Why? For the Eden I envision, of course...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Perhaps, as much as it pains me to admit it. Maybe that\\'s why... we\\'re similar.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'A naive idealist.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: '...Like you.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'As long as there are humans like you, I guess the world is not beyond saving.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
